  "markup": "Dr. Christopher Carraway of LTU interviews David Baxter TD, BSc(HONS), DPhil, MBA, Dean of the School of Physiotherapy-University of Otasgo, New Zealand at the NAALT/WALT joint meeting in Washington, DC September 2014 for his views on current LLLT research and combined conference. Dr. Baxter was a speaker during Thematic Session III.\u0026nbsp;"
